  "title": "ToggleValue Type from connectToggleRefinement no longer exists",
  "body": "## 🐛 Bug description\r\nI switched from the experimental Typescript version back to the mainstream version after typings were released in the main version and now I am no long able to `import type { ToggleValue } from 'instantsearch.js/es/connectors/toggle-refinement/connectToggleRefinement';` because it doesn't exist as seen in the screenshot below showing connectToggleRefinement.d.ts.\r\n\r\n## 🖥 Screenshot\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/7559478/130681882-9b656330-2c9a-4070-9b6d-22843649e581.png)\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\"instantsearch.js\": \"4.28.0\",",
